  <brief_title>Phase I Study of Sorafenib Dosed Continuously With Cyclophosphamide and Doxorubicin</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase I Open-label, Non-randomized, Non-placebo Controlled Study to Determine the Safety, Pharmacokinetics, and Tumor Response Profile of Sorafenib as Continuous Dosing in Combination With Cyclophosphamide and Doxorubicin in Patients With Advanced, Refractory Solid Tumors</official_title>
